text: Carmine Luppino (born 10 January 1948) is a retired Italian gymnast. He competed at the 1972 Olympics in all artistic gymnastics events and finished in 16th place with the Italian team. His best individual result was 60th place on the parallel bars. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Gymnasts at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Italian male artistic gymnasts
